<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.9">
<l>iṭaki lēṉōṉ ṟaṭṭa killē ṉaimpulaṉ vellakillēṉ</l>
<l>kaṭava ṉākik kālan tōṟum pūppaṟit tēttakillēṉ</l>
<l>maṭava ṉeñcaṅ kātal kūra valviṉai yēṉayarppāy</l>
<l>taṭavu kiṉṟē ṉeṅkuk kāṇpaṉ cakkarat taṇṇalaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I cannot put, I cannot place one thing, I cannot vanquish the five senses,</l>
<l>being under an obligation, I cannot all the time pluck flowers [and] praise,</l>
<l>While the heart of me fool is full of love, I with harsh karma forgetfully</l>
<l>grope –  where shall I see the majesty with the discus?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
